rotate_left
description:
Rotate tree left.
(see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tree_rotation)

     A                B
    / \              / \
   a   B     ->     A   c
      / \          / \
     b   c        a   b

name: src/rotate/rotate_right.js
rotate_right
description:
Rotate tree right.
(see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tree_rotation)

     B                A
    / \              / \
   A   c     ->     a   B
  / \                  / \
 a   b                b   c
